      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY WEE LASS (2) scored two back with ease when racing on speed but drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 2 length 5th at this track (16.02). Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can atone. WOW PARTY TIME (8) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing second (15.83) and beaten a nose over 272m at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to be in this for a long way. KISS AND RUN (7) is a quick dog who thrives over the short dashes. Scored over 272m at this track last time in a Grade 5 (15.73). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Must be included in calculations.",
